Synopsis: Players have just casted Dispel Evil and Good: Break Enchantment on Oskar, and for a shot while he is free from the effects of the possession, although the source of the evil that haunts him is not destroyed. He will give some information to players pointing to his previous actions before the possession, variously Mystic Carrion, the atelier, and the cursed paint. His words are hoarse and laboured - the ghost possessing him has been screaming and shouting. If Jannath is present she will interject at the beginning
